<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77d8ec34-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s71"><num value="71">§ 71.</num><heading> “Person” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">When used in this subchapter the term “person” includes partnerships, corporations, and associations.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77d8ec35-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1916-09-08/ch463">Sept. 8, 1916, ch. 463</ref>, title VIII, § 800, <ref href="/us/stat/39/798">39 Stat. 798</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
